1 - GENERATE PAIR KEY          - openssl genrsa -out keypair.pem 2048

2 - OBTAIN PUBLIC KEY  (JAVA)  - openssl rsa -in keypair.pem -outform DER -pubout -out public.der

3 - OBTAIN PRIVATE KEY (JAVA)  - openssl pkcs8 -topk8 -nocrypt -in keypair.pem -outform DER -out private.der

4 - GENERATE CSR               - openssl req -new -key keypair.pem -out server.csr

5 - GENERATE SELF-SIGNED CERT  - openssl x509 -req -days 365 -in server.csr -signkey keypair.pem -out server.crt
